uk.ac.ox.cs.diadem.oxpath.output

Class AAdvancedCustomOutputHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.ox.cs.diadem.oxpath.output.ACustomOutputHandler
      • uk.ac.ox.cs.diadem.oxpath.output.AAdvancedCustomOutputHandler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IAbstractOutputHandler, IOutputHandler

    public abstract class AAdvancedCustomOutputHandler
extends ACustomOutputHandler
    This abstract class gives the possibilty to execute procesuder just before the first output node and just after the output of the last node. It also returns the time spent for the output.
    Author:
    Ruslan Fayzrakhmanov Jun 18, 2016
